<section class="mbr-section article mbr-section__container" id="content1-2e" style="background-color: rgb(255, 203, 8); padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom: 0px;">

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 lead"><p>Glovtex Oil &amp; Gas Limited is an engineering company specializing in the development of Telco (Core/IN, Rollout and Maintenance) solutions for the GSM and wireless communication industry.  It also serves in various engineering constructions and oil serving in several fields. We are dedicated to offering a customer-centric approach to Technology projects, implementations and constructions in vivid contract to the more traditional approach.  Glovtex Oil &amp; Gas Limited serves several companies, all dominant players in their sectors: Telecom vendors, Service Providers, Mobile Operators, construction companies and other Information &amp; Communication businesses.</p><p><br></p><p>The operations of the company are fully departmentalized with each department handling a single specialized operation by experienced technical personnel with supportive staff. Our Project Managers coordinate and supervise at our field/site operations. We have highly skilled and experienced individuals ensuring that deadlines are met in an efficient, but cost effective manner. Our working standards (methodologies) are of the highest quality following detailed standards.</p><p><br></p><p>Our mission is to earn, through dedication and hard work, a reputation of being the most reliable and efficient organization in our chosen field. We understand the importance of partnership and are committed to provide Global Solutions that maximize Business Telecommunication Assets; helping you to achieve your goals from basic deployment and roadmap, design and architecture, implementation and development to Operations &amp; Support.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p></div>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>

